lead_paragraph: Tynice Martin had a career-high 28 points and No. 19 West Virginia beat North Carolina A&T 80-64 in the first night of the Savannah Invitational on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Tynice Martin's 28 Leads No. 19 West Virginia Over NC A&T
